channel.title: Requesting a background
channel.description:
I'd like to request a background for a friend. The background is meant for a youtube channel. You get pretty much carte blanc, it should just be abstract, preferably in the theme of electronic/hardstyle music. The name is HardDubFM, which should be fun to see on the background as well obviously.
So if you're bored and have some PS skills, do an attempt please. It'd be greatly appreciated.
Thanks in advance.
